<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Criminal
Law Class Notes </span><st1:date Year="2003" Day="8" Month="9"><span
 style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>9/8/03</span></st1:date><span
