</span></span></span><![endif]><span dir=LTR><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Was there <i>conduct</i> involved here?<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l18 level1 lfo16;
tab-stops:list .5in'><![if !supportLists]><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
