<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Would
retributivists favor a <i>mens rea</i> requirement in the law?<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>Yes.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>�
</span>They would be offended by a justice system that punishes without finding
