<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Under
this definition, shouldn�t Cunningham be found guilty?<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>Sure!<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>�
</span>But the appellate court tells us that the jury instructions were
