<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>So,
remember: <i>malice means intentional or reckless</i>.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>It <i>doesn�t</i> mean �wicked�.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>In
this case, did the trial court use the culpability approach or the elemental
