<p><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Morris
wrote a worm that wasn�t meant to be damaging, but was.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>He was convicted and punished of a relatively
lenient sentence.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Morris
doesn�t deny his actions, but he says that the word �intentionally� applies to
each part of the crime, and thus the prosecution must prove he intentionally
