computer.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>This
is a common question of real-world lawyering.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>�
</span>How do we interpret this statute?<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>�
</span>The trial court said this statute is unambiguous, while the appellate
