<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>The
prosecution would like to see a semi-colon between the first phrase with
�intent� and the second bit that talks about �conduct� that �alters, damages,
or destroys information�.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>As a lawyer,
