<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>If
it used to say �(1) knowledge, (2) knowledge� and now it says �(1) intent, (2)
nothing�, we think they meant only for the first element to require a <i>mens
rea</i>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Keep
in mind that Congress has not adopted the Model Penal Code into the U.S. Code.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>The
problem of Y (Note 3, pp. 154-155)</span></b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Y
provided false information to Lockheed in connection with a Department of
