<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Let�s
say the Model Penal Code <i>was</i> applicable in the federal system.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>What would be the result?<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>What
does the statute say?<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>The word knowingly
is stuck right in the middle of the statute, and if I were the prosecutor, I
