<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>The
Model Penal Code drafters don�t like the idea of ever punishing a person whose
culpability is mere negligence.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>If a
