dir=LTR><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Mens Rea<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l31 level1 lfo20;
