<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>There
are very few cases in the real world like the last hypothetical.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>In real life, D and X are probably working in
concert.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>This comes up more in tort
