<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>There
are very different perceptions of the police in different segments of
society.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>Some people always believe the
