<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><i><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>If
we�re going to talk about negligence, and we�re going to talk about whether or
not the Williamses lived up to an objective standard of behavior, should we
