style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>�This
is an area of the law that is in deep flux.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>�
</span>This is where lawyers make their money.�<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>If
the answer is that yes�we�ll consider the Williamses� situation�the defense may
put on evidence that would explain the experience of being on a reservation and
the concerns that Indians may have that other people may not have.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>If the answer is no�the standard is purely
