<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>We
could decide that one of the above items is relevant and not the other.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>It�s not all or nothing. <span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>�</span>But once we go from a purely objective
