<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>In
light of what we�re trying to evaluate, why do we need this information?<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Besides
the issue of whether or not the Williamses were negligent, what else is
critically necessary to determine whether the Williamses should be
punished?<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>There�s a proximate cause
