<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>If
we assume that any reasonable person would have taken the child to the doctor <i>before</i>
the Williamses did, we need to know when it would have been too late to save
the child�s life.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>In other words, if a
