<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Dressler
says that this often happens in the adversarial system.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>When you have to take a position that
initially runs against your values, the dissonance that results becomes so
