<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Estrich
again<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>A couple
of things to understand about the Estrich piece:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>This
article was made into a book written for lay people.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>In the book version of this article, Estrich
told the story of the fact that she herself had been raped.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>Estrich is on TV pretty frequently.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>She was the chairman for the presidential
campaign for Michael Dukakis.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>She
