</span></span></span><![endif]><span dir=LTR><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>The spousal immunity rule is eliminated.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>Husbands are not protected from being
convicted of sexual assault against their wives.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>A husband who committed the same acts stated
in this case against his wife would be just as guilty as M.T.S.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l21 level1 lfo28;
tab-stops:list .5in'><![if !supportLists]><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
