<p><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-style:italic'>Rape shield laws</span></b><span style='font-size:
14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-style:italic'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-style:italic'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-style:italic'>The basics � Here�s the problem these laws are
designed to fight: the defense will try to get a bunch of evidence out to try
to make the alleged victim look like a �slut�.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>�
</span>It can be argued that this evidence is relevant because it would go to
