<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-style:italic'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>This
will be awful for the woman.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>Also, why
would a woman ever report the crime?<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>We
might admit evidence that the woman in the Kobe Bryant case had consensual sex
on other occasions, but under rape shield laws, we won�t admit evidence that
