<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Model
Penal Code � 3.04</span></b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
12.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>When
one provision of a statute refers to another provision, you must consult both
