<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>If
an actor�s belief is sincere but reckless or negligent, the actor isn�t
justified as far as reckless or negligent offenses.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>If the defendant was <i>negligent</i> in
believing that a toy gun was actually real, then under the Model Penal Code the
