<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><b><i><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><a
href="peoplevgoetz.htm">People v. Goetz</a><o:p></o:p></span></i></b></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>The
four victims got on a subway to </span><st1:City><st1:place><span
  style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Manhattan</span></st1:place></st1:City><span
