<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>The
Court of Appeals of </span><st1:State><st1:place><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
  mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>New York</span></st1:place></st1:State><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'> rules that the statute was
