</span>They might have also just nullified.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>What
is a reasonable belief?<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>What
facts are relevant in deciding whether Goetz�s belief was reasonable?<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>Goetz didn�t know that the victims were armed
with screwdrivers.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>That was a �lucky
