<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Do
the races of the defendant and victims matter?<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>What�s
the deal with the five dollars?<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>It
depends on the context.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>In </span><st1:City><st1:place><span
  style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>New York City</span></st1:place></st1:City><span
