<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>How
can it be justifiable to kill an objectively innocent person?<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>We might excuse someone for it, but maybe it
wouldn�t be justified.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>The common law
