<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Is
this a good result?<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>What would feminists
say?<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>Wouldn�t it depend on whether you
