<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>If
North Carolina applies the common law, why isn�t Norman entitled to a
self-defense claim?<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>It rests on the
