<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>The
attorney was a private attorney, but the woman was not wealth.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>Women�s groups raised funds for her to pay
the attorney.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>The women�s groups told
the attorney that he shouldn�t claim insanity, but rather self-defense.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>The groups were sensitive to the distinction
between justification and excuse.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>They
