style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>They didn�t want the woman to be seen as
crazy.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>That�s an excuse for doing
something <i>wrong</i>.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>The groups
