it is a �<i>person of reasonable firmness</i>� standard.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>It�s an objective rather than a subjective
standard.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><b><i><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><a
