<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Inchoate<a
style='mso-footnote-id:ftn14' href="#_ftn14" name="_ftnref14" title=""><span
class=MsoFootnoteReference><span style='mso-special-character:footnote'><![if !supportFootnotes]><span
class=MsoFootnoteReference><b><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman";
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:
EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'>[14]</span></b></span><![endif]></span></span></a>
offenses</span></b><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>So
far, we�ve been looking at completed offenses.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>�
</span>Now we�re going to look at incomplete or failed offenses.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Consider
the range of conduct:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l13 level1 lfo37;
tab-stops:list .5in'><![if !supportLists]><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>1.<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><span
dir=LTR><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Someone <i>thinks</i>
about committing a crime (we don�t punish this).<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l13 level1 lfo37;
tab-stops:list .5in'><![if !supportLists]><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>2.<span
