dir=LTR><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>Someone <i>conspires
</i>to commit a crime.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l13 level1 lfo37;
tab-stops:list .5in'><![if !supportLists]><span style='font-size:14.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>4.<span
