style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>They say he basically acted purposely.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>We have a split.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>The Model Penal Code gives us an answer by
having the word �belief� in there.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>The
