<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>This
is the final step in the semester.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>We�ve
been talking about single people committing crimes to this point.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>Now we look at the extraordinarily common
problem that most crimes involve more than one person.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>Who else besides the �trigger man� is also
