<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt'>It�s
obvious if you �pull the trigger� that you�re responsible.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>But who else should be held responsible for
something they did not do?<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>� </span>That�s the
